<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>自动化 on Billy's Blog</title><link>https://virgoC0der.github.io/tags/%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96/</link><description>Recent content in 自动化 on Billy's Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><managingEditor>billychen826@gmail.com (Billy)</managingEditor><webMaster>billychen826@gmail.com (Billy)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://virgoC0der.github.io/tags/%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Claude+MCP一键生成博客：AI助力内容创作与自动化部署</title><link>https://virgoC0der.github.io/posts/claude-mcp-blog-automation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>billychen826@gmail.com (Billy)</author><guid>https://virgoC0der.github.io/posts/claude-mcp-blog-automation/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="claudemcp一键生成博客ai助力内容创作与自动化部署">Claude+MCP一键生成博客：AI助力内容创作与自动化部署&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>在这个信息爆炸的时代，高效地创建和发布内容已成为许多创作者的迫切需求。今天，我想分享一个结合了AI大语言模型Claude和Model Context Protocol (MCP)的强大工作流，它可以让你以惊人的速度从创意到发布完成整个博客创作过程。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="工作流概述">工作流概述&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>这个一键式博客生成和部署流程包含三个主要步骤：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>使用Claude生成高质量的博客内容并保存为Markdown文件&lt;/li>
&lt;li>通过MCP desktop-commander自动推送到GitHub仓库并触发GitHub Actions&lt;/li>
&lt;li>利用MCP playwright自动检查部署结果&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>这个过程完全自动化，从内容创建到部署验证，几乎不需要人工干预。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="配置mcp工具">配置MCP工具&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>要开始使用这个工作流，首先需要在Claude客户端中配置MCP工具。步骤如下：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>打开Claude客户端&lt;/li>
&lt;li>点击Settings -&amp;gt; Developer -&amp;gt; Edit Config&lt;/li>
&lt;li>输入以下配置：&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;mcpServers&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;fileSystme&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;command&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;npx&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;args&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: [
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;-y&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;YOUR PATH&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> ]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> },
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;playwright&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;command&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;npx&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;args&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: [
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;@playwright/mcp@latest&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> ]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> },
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;desktop-commander&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;command&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;npx&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;#34;args&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: [
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;-y&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;@smithery/cli@latest&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;run&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;@wonderwhy-er/desktop-commander&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;--key&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;YOUR PERSONAL KEY&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> ]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> }
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>这个配置告诉Claude如何与三个关键MCP工具通信：&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>